pma:database.name: finalproject
pma:database.pma:table: CREATE TABLE `attendance` ( `a_id` int(10) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT, `std_id` int(10) NOT NULL, `date` varchar(50) NOT NULL, `time` varchar(50) NOT NULL, PRIMARY KEY (`a_id`), KEY `std_id` (`std_id`) ) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=544 DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8mb4;

CREATE TABLE `semester` ( `sem_id` int(10) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT, `name` varchar(50) NOT NULL, `faculty_id` int(10) NOT NULL, PRIMARY KEY (`sem_id`), KEY `faculty_id` (`faculty_id`), CONSTRAINT `semester_ibfk_1` FOREIGN KEY (`faculty_id`) REFERENCES `faculty` (`f_id`) ) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=10 DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8mb4;

CREATE TABLE `student` ( `std_id` int(10) NOT NULL, `fullname` varchar(100) NOT NULL, `faculty_id` int(10) NOT NULL, `semester_id` int(10) NOT NULL, PRIMARY KEY (`std_id`), KEY `faculty_id` (`faculty_id`), KEY `semester_id` (`semester_id`), CONSTRAINT `student_ibfk_1` FOREIGN KEY (`faculty_id`) REFERENCES `faculty` (`f_id`), CONSTRAINT `student_ibfk_2` FOREIGN KEY (`semester_id`) REFERENCES `semester` (`sem_id`) ) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8mb4;
